Class NonLockable

java.lang.Object
  org.talend.core.model.temp.NonLockable

Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractSerializable, DefaultProcessImpl
public abstract class NonLockable
extends java.lang.Object
implements ILockable

Convenience abstract class used to manage a non implementation of ILockable interface. Class wich implements correspond to ILockable interface contract but cannot be locked.
